{"data":[{"name":"81:1","price":"1. Apabila matahari digulung,","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلشَّمۡسُ كُوِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5801,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:2","price":"2. Dan apabila bintang-bintang berjatuhan,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5802,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:3","price":"3. Dan apabila gunung-gunung dihancurkan,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5803,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:4","price":"4. Dan apabila unta-unta yang bunting ditinggalkan (tidak terurus),","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5804,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:5","price":"5. Dan apabila binatang-binatang liar dikumpulkan,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5805,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:6","price":"6. Dan apabila lautan dipanaskan,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5806,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:7","price":"7. Dan apabila ruh-ruh dipertemukan (dengan tubuh),","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5807,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:8","price":"8. Dan apabila bayi-bayi perempuan yang dikubur hidup-hidup ditanya,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡمَوۡءُۥدَةُ سُئِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5808,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:9","price":"9. Karena dosa apa dia dibunuh?","arabic":"بِأَيِّ ذَنۢبٖ قُتِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5809,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:10","price":"10. Dan apabila lembaran-lembaran (catatan amal) telah dibuka lebar-lebar,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5810,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:11","price":"11. Dan apabila langit dilenyapkan,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5811,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:12","price":"12. Dan apabila neraka Jahim dinyalakan,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5812,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:13","price":"13. Dan apabila surga didekatkan,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَنَّةُ أُزۡلِفَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5813,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:14","price":"14. Setiap jiwa akan mengetahui apa yang telah dikerjakannya.","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّآ أَحۡضَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5814,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:15","price":"15. Aku bersumpah demi bintang-bintang,","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلۡخُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5815,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:16","price":"16. Yang beredar dan terbenam,","arabic":"ٱلۡجَوَارِ ٱلۡكُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5816,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:17","price":"17. Demi malam apabila telah larut,","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا عَسۡعَسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5817,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:18","price":"18. Dan demi subuh apabila fajar telah menyingsing,","arabic":"وَٱلصُّبۡحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5818,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:19","price":"19. Sesungguhnya (Al-Qur`ān) itu benar-benar firman (Allah yang dibawa oleh) utusan yang mulia (Jibril),","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلُ رَسُولٖ كَرِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5819,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:20","price":"20. yang memiliki kekuatan, memiliki kedudukan tinggi di sisi (Allah) yang memiliki Arasy,","arabic":"ذِي قُوَّةٍ عِندَ ذِي ٱلۡعَرۡشِ مَكِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5820,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:21","price":"21. Yang di sana (di alam malaikat) ditaati dan dipercaya.","arabic":"مُّطَاعٖ ثَمَّ أَمِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5821,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:22","price":"22. Dan temanmu (Muhammad) itu bukanlah orang gila.","arabic":"وَمَا صَاحِبُكُم بِمَجۡنُونٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5822,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:23","price":"23. Dan sungguh, dia (Muhammad) telah melihatnya (Jibril) di ufuk yang terang.","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡمُبِينِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5823,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:24","price":"24. Dan Dia (Muhammad) bukanlah seorang yang kikir (enggan) untuk menerangkan yang gaib.","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ٱلۡغَيۡبِ بِضَنِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5824,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:25","price":"25. Dan (Al-Qur`ān) itu bukanlah perkataan setan yang terkutuk,","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوۡلِ شَيۡطَٰنٖ رَّجِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5825,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:26","price":"26. Maka ke manakah kamu akan pergi?*(899)","arabic":"فَأَيۡنَ تَذۡهَبُونَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5826,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*899). Setelah diterangkan bahwa Al-Qur`ān itu benar-benar datang dari Allah dan di dalamnya ada pelajaran dan  petunjuk yang memimpin manusia ke jalan yang lurus, ditanyakanlah kepada orang-orang kafir itu, “Jalan manakah yang akan kamu tempuh lagi?”","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:27","price":"27. (Al-Qur`ān) itu tidak lain adalah peringatan bagi seluruh alam,","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرٞ لِّلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5827,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:28","price":"28. (Yaitu) bagi siapa di antara kamu yang menghendaki menempuh jalan yang lurus.","arabic":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمۡ أَن يَسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5828,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"81:29","price":"29. Dan kamu tidak dapat menghendaki (menempuh jalan itu) kecuali apabila dikehendaki Allah, Tuhan seluruh alam.","arabic":"وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5829,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir","Chapter At-Takwir","Takwir","Surah Takwir","Chapter Takwir","At Takwir","Surah At Takwir","Chapter At Takwir","Surah 81","Chapter 81","The Overthrowing","التكوير"]}